<span id="freeTextContainer6732025317926496862">Knowing this the last in the series I held off reading it as long as possible and therefore was grateful for the insertions of back story. And what a story - really breathtaking action, beautiful, original descriptions and told in a way which enabled me to totally immerse myself in the same manner I did as a child. For which I am grateful.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

