<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/404828.Dreaming_the_Hound"><img alt="Dreaming the Hound (Boudica, #3)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1174464357l/404828._SY75_.jpg" />
